<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Liste_des_bourgmestres">Liste des bourgmestres</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Evere&amp;veaction=edit&amp;vesection=21" title="Modifier la section : Liste des bourgmestres" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor">modifier</a><span class="mw-editsection-divider"> | </span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Evere&amp;action=edit&amp;section=21" title="Modifier la section : Liste des bourgmestres">modifier le code</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
